==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|responsibilit|ies}}

# The state of being [[responsible]], [[accountable]], or [[answerable]].
#: '''''Responsibility''' is a heavy burden.''
# A [[duty]], [[obligation]] or [[liability]] for which someone is responsible or accountable.
#: ''Keeping this system under control is everyone's '''responsibility'''.''
#: ''Why didn't you clean the house? That was your '''responsibility'''!''

